        "# Create and Reshape a Tensor\n",
        "\n",
        "Create a tensor containing integers from `0` to `23` and reshape it to `(3, 2, 4)`.\n",
        "\n",
        "Tasks:\n",
        "\n",
        "1. Print the tensor.\n",
        "2. Print rank and shape.\n",
        "3. Print dtype."
      ],
      "id": "9a8e2276"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "#| eval: false\n",
        "# Your code here\n",
        "raw = torch.arange(24)\n",
        "t = raw.reshape(3, 2, 4)\n",
        "\n",
        "print(t)\n",
        "print(\"rank:\", t.ndim)\n",
        "print(\"shape:\", t.shape)\n",
        "print(\"dtype:\", t.dtype)"
      ],
      "id": "a192d56d",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "# Indexing and Reductions\n",
        "\n",
        "Using tensor `t` from Question 1:\n",
        "\n",
        "1. Extract the first 2D block (`t[0]`).\n",
        "2. Compute column sums of that block.\n",
        "3. Compute row means of that block."
      ],
      "id": "49e750a2"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "#| eval: false\n",
        "# Your code here\n",
        "block = t[0]\n",
        "print(\"block:\\n\", block)\n",
        "print(\"column sums:\", block.sum(dim=0))\n",
        "print(\"row means:\", block.float().mean(dim=1))"
      ],
      "id": "b2b03baa",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
